      "bgColor": "#080b08",
      "bgGradient": "linear-gradient(160deg,#020602 0%,#040d04 100%)",
      "bgImage": "",
      "titleText": "Log Analysis",
      "titleColor": "#00ff41",
      "titleSize": 48,
      "subtitleText": "",
      "subtitleColor": "#2a6b3a",
      "bodyText": "",
      "bodyColor": "#7ab87a",
      "bodySize": 22,
      "bullets": [],
      "codeText": "# Linux auth logs\ngrep \"Failed password\" /var/log/auth.log\ngrep \"Accepted password\" /var/log/auth.log\n\n# Apache/Nginx access log\nawk '{print $1}' access.log | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head  # top IPs\ngrep \"POST\" access.log | grep -v \"200\"\n\n# Windows Event logs (on Linux)\npython-evtx viewer or:\nevtxdump.py Security.evtx | grep -i \"EventID>4625\"   # failed logins\nEventID 4624 = Logon success\nEventID 4625 = Logon failure\nEventID 4688 = Process creation",
      "codeLang": "bash",
      "imageUrl": "",
      "showTitle": true,
      "showSubtitle": false,
